"Caution the Transmitter to guide you away from obstacles over which you might stumble, or which you might overturn.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Tell him that you place yourself in his hands for protection, and then endeavor to think no more about the matter, for such thought tends to distract your passivity.",1,1,0,1,1,0
"The above feats or demonstrations are all performed along the same general lines as indicated a little further back, and all are capable of being accomplished by anyone of ordinary intelligence, with a little study, care and practice.",0,0,0,0,0,0
