THE WIRE CONTACT.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"A sensational and effective method of performing some of the simpler feats is performed by some public performers, and consists in having a piece of thick wire, about one foot in length grasped by the Receiver's left hand, and by the Transmitter's right hand, instead of the ordinary contact.",1,0,0,0,0,0
