THE SIMPLER METHOD.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"A simpler method of performing the feats and demonstrations which we have styled The More Difficult Feats, is that of having the Transmitter stand by your right side, turning toward you and placing his right hand over yours, _the tips of his fingers_ resting on your fingers _between your large knuckles and first joints_, (instead of standing on your left side with his fingers grasped in your left hand, as heretofore mentioned).",1,1,0,1,1,0
