THE AUTOMATIC WRITING EXPERIMENTS.,0,0,0,0,0,0
"Another way of conducting experiments along the lines of the Higher Phenomena of Mind Reading, is akin to the Automatic Writing known to all students of Occultism.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"The Transmitter concentrates his thought and Will in the usual manner, while the Receiver places himself in the usual receptive, passive state of mind, and awaits the impressions.",1,1,1,1,1,1
"But instead of the Receiver merely sitting as usual, he draws his chair to a table, having a soft pencil in his hand and a pad of paper on the table before him.",1,1,0,1,1,0
"He holds the pencil lightly between his fingers, with its point touching the paper--and then awaits impressions.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"Under good conditions, after waiting a time the pencil will begin to twitch and move feebly.",0,0,0,0,0,0
The hands and fingers should allow it full and free motion.,0,0,0,0,0,0
